Exploratory Volatility Calculations

February 20, 2020

30 Companies

Data collected from WRDS CRSP Database.

data$COMNAM[data$COMNAM == 'WAL MART STORES INC'] <- 'WALMART INC'

comnames

Oracle

# making the data into time series plots

summary(oracle.p.t)
